title: Dr. Brown's - Happy Feeding™
description:
It begins the moment you find out...

Unforgettable adventures lie ahead.

In the beginning your little one will keep you on a lively schedule.

Every day, you learn more about one another...trying your best to remember each and every moment.

Sure…some days can be more interesting than others…but you wouldn’t have it any other way. 

As the seasons change and you watch them grow you will wonder where all the time went.

And more than once, you’ll catch yourself saying “Look at the miracle we made.”  

After all, there is no one like your baby. 

And at the end of each day you can rest easy knowing you’ve given them the best of everything.  

You also know, deep in your heart...the best is yet to come

Dr. Brown's
Happy feeding.
